OL,3,CClose to 400 deaths caused by alcohol
OL,4,Cin NI in 2024
OL,6,FThere were close to 400 alcohol-
OL,7,Fspecific deaths registered in Northern
OL,8,FIreland in 2024, new statistics have
OL,9,Fshown.
OL,11,FThe number of deaths caused by alcohol
OL,12,Fin the region has risen by 81.3% in a
OL,13,Fdecade, from 219 in 2014 to 397 in
OL,14,F2024.
OL,16,FThe British Medical Association
OL,17,Fdescribed the latest figures as
OL,18,F"alarming" and said they showed that
OL,19,Fminimum unit alcohol pricing
OL,20,Flegislation is needed in Northern
OL,21,FIreland.
