OL,3,CClose to 400 deaths caused by alcohol
OL,4,Cin NI in 2024
OL,6,FThe report from the Northern Ireland
OL,7,FStatistics and Research Agency (Nisra)
OL,8,Fmeasures deaths from conditions known
OL,9,Fto be exclusively caused by alcohol.
OL,11,FIn 2024, almost two-thirds (64.5%) of
OL,12,Fthe 397 deaths were men.
OL,14,FThe report said males accounted for
OL,15,F65.9% of alcohol-specific deaths
OL,16,Fregistered between 2014 and 2024.
OL,18,FThe alcohol-specific death rate for
OL,19,Fmen in 2024 was 28.1 deaths per
OL,20,F100,000 population, and 14.9 for women.
