OL,3,CClose to 400 deaths caused by alcohol
OL,4,Cin NI in 2024
OL,6,FThe figures indicate that between 2014
OL,7,Fand 2024, the alcohol-specific
OL,8,Fmortality rate for men increased by
OL,9,F51.1%, from 18.6 to 28.1 per 100,000.
OL,11,FThe rate for women increased by
OL,12,F104.1%, from 7.3 per 100,000 to 14.9.
OL,14,FNisra said that alcohol-specific
OL,15,Fdeaths were more prevalent among the
OL,16,F45-54 and 55-64 age groups, which
OL,17,Ftogether accounted for 59.4% of all of
OL,18,Fthose deaths registered in 2024.
