OL,3,CClose to 400 deaths caused by alcohol
OL,4,Cin NI in 2024
OL,6,FIn 2024, Belfast Local Government
OL,7,FDistrict had the highest rate of
OL,8,Falcohol-specific deaths of all areas
OL,9,Fin Northern Ireland at 31.1 per
OL,10,F100,000 population, followed by Derry
OL,11,FCity and Strabane (25.6).
OL,13,FThe lowest rate in 2024 was recorded
OL,14,Ffor Mid Ulster (12.0).
OL,16,FLooking over a five-year period, Nisra
OL,17,Fsaid there were almost four times as
OL,18,Fmany alcohol-specific deaths in the
OL,19,Fmost deprived areas compared with the
OL,20,Fleast deprived areas.
