OL,3,CClose to 400 deaths caused by alcohol
OL,4,Cin NI in 2024
OL,6,FDr Clodagh Corrigan, deputy chair of
OL,7,FBMA's Northern Ireland Council, said:
OL,8,F"These figures are alarming.
OL,10,F"Doctors see first-hand the
OL,11,Fdevastating effects of prolonged
OL,12,Falcohol abuse on the health of their
OL,13,Fpatients as it is one of the most
OL,14,Fsignificant risk factors for
OL,15,Fcardiovascular health, cancer and
OL,16,Fmental health.
OL,18,F"This is why minimum unit alcohol
OL,19,Fpricing (MUP) legislation is needed in
OL,20,FNorthern Ireland.
